data.description: Fixer duplex! Bring your vision to life and enjoy country living with this delightful 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom per side. Nestled on an expansive 0.55-acre lot. Bring your vision to life with what this property has to offer! With room for RV parking and showcasing breathtaking countryside views, you'll relish the tranquility of this serene location. The spacious backyard provides ample space for outdoor activities, and a convenient tool shed adds functionality. This property presents a fantastic investment opportunity with rental potential, making it a wise choice for both investors and those seeking a peaceful, nature-inspired retreat. Don't miss your chance to own this slice of country paradise!
